209
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,030
<i>I put them away,</i>

210
00:14:58,110 --> 00:15:00,740
<i>and they're to be yours.</i>

211
00:15:09,820 --> 00:15:12,080
<i>- Good night, Scout.
- Good night.</i>

212
00:15:22,170 --> 00:15:24,430
<i>- [ Atticus ] Good night, Jem.
- [ Jem ] Good night.</i>

213
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:40,780
<i>- Jem?
- [ Jem ] Yes?</i>

214
00:15:43,190 --> 00:15:48,450
<i>- [ Sighs ]
