216
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:55,800
<i>- Old as I am now?
- Mm-hmm.</i>

217
00:15:58,030 --> 00:16:01,970
<i>- Was Mama pretty?
- Mm-hmm.</i>

218
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:05,240
<i>[ Scout ]
Was Mama nice?</i>

219
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:08,400
<i>[ Jem ]
Mm-hmm.</i>

220
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:12,240
<i>- Did you love her?
- Yes.</i>

221
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:16,580
<i>- Did I love her?
- Mm-hmm.</i>

222
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:22,590
<i>- Do you miss her?
- Mm-hmm.</i>

223
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,760
<i>[ Footsteps Approaching ]</i>

224
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:35,830
<i>- [ Man ] Evening, Atticus.
