225
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:40,870
<i>Rather warm, isn't it?</i>

226
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:42,940
<i>Yes, indeed.</i>

227
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:50,120
<i>How's Mrs. Taylor?</i>

228
00:16:50,190 --> 00:16:52,780
<i>She's fine.
