257
00:19:27,540 --> 00:19:29,570
<i>Come on, Scout.</i>

258
00:19:36,690 --> 00:19:39,090
<i>Run for your life, Scout!</i>

259
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:41,420
<i>Come on, Dill!</i>

260
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:50,600
