261
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:55,970
<i>You tell them about this back
in Meridian County, Mr. Dill Harris.</i>

262
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:58,270
<i>I'll tell you what let's do.</i>

263
00:19:58,340 --> 00:20:02,280
<i>Let's go down to the courthouse and see
