271
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:31,970
<i>He's a lawyer,
and he has a case.</i>

272
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:34,480
<i>The grand jury is charging
his client today.</i>

273
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:37,480
<i>I heard something about it last night
when Judge Taylor came over.</i>

274
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:40,640
<i>- Let's go watch.
- No, Dill.</i>

275
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:43,710
<i>- He wouldn't like that. Dill!
- Dill!</i>

276
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:48,480
<i>[ Jem, Hushed ]
Dill, wait a minute.</i>

277
00:20:50,390 --> 00:20:52,330
<i>Shh.</i>

278
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:54,490
<i>- [ Typing ]
- Is that the courtroom?</i>

279
00:20:54,560 --> 00:20:57,330
<i>[ Whispers ]
Yeah. Shh.</i>

280
00:21:01,070 --> 00:21:03,770
<i>- I can't see anything.
- Shh.</i>

281
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:07,780
<i>Y'all lift me up
so I can see what's going on.</i>

282
00:21:07,840 --> 00:21:10,940
<i>- All right.
- Make a saddle, Scout.</i>

283
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:18,450
<i>Not much is happenin'.</i>

284
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:21,750
<i>The judge looks like
