285
00:21:21,820 --> 00:21:24,120
<i>[ Groaning ]</i>

286
00:21:24,190 --> 00:21:27,130
<i>I see your daddy
and a colored man.</i>

287
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:30,100
<i>- The colored man--
