289
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:36,600
<i>- [ Man ] I seen him with Mayella.
- I wonder what he's done
to cry about?</i>

290
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:38,400
<i>What's going on?</i>

291
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:43,310
<i>There's a whole lot of men
sittin' together on one side,</i>

292
00:21:43,380 --> 00:21:47,370
<i>and one man keeps pointin'
at the colored man and yellin'.</i>

293
00:21:47,450 --> 00:21:50,150
