his story against ourn."</i>

317
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:20,280
<i>Well, they was wrong,
wasn't they?</i>

318
00:23:20,340 --> 00:23:22,780
<i>I've been appointed
to defend Tom Robinson.</i>

319
00:23:22,850 --> 00:23:26,440
<i>Now that he's been charged,
that's what I intend to do.</i>

320
00:23:26,520 --> 00:23:29,780
<i>- You taking his story--
- If you'll excuse me, Mr. Ewell.</i>

321
00:23:34,190 --> 00:23:37,280
<i>What kind of man are you?</i>

322
00:23:37,360 --> 00:23:39,950
<i>You got children of your own.</i>

323
00:23:41,860 --> 00:23:45,460
<i>[ Radio ]</i>

324
00:23:45,540 --> 00:23:49,230
<i>[ Dill Whispering ]
