325
00:23:59,220 --> 00:24:02,310
<i>I think we ought to stay right here
in Miss Stephanie's yard.</i>

326
00:24:02,390 --> 00:24:05,580
<i>You don't have to come along...
Angel May.</i>

327
00:24:20,340 --> 00:24:23,600
<i>What are you gonna do?</i>

328
00:24:23,670 --> 00:24:26,270
<i>[ Hushed ] Gonna look in a window
at the Radley house...</i>

329
00:24:26,340 --> 00:24:29,440
<i>and see if we can get
a look at Boo Radley!</i>

330
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:31,840
<i>Come on, Dill.</i>

331
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:38,620
<i>- Jem, please, I'm scared.
- Then go home if you're scared!</i>

332
00:24:38,690 --> 00:24:41,210
<i>I swear, Scout, you act
more like a girl all the time.</i>

333
00:24:41,290 --> 00:24:43,450
<i>- Come on, Dill.
- Wait for me. I'm coming.</i>

334
00:24:43,530 --> 00:24:45,460
<i>Shh.</i>

335
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:52,130
<i>We'll go around back...</i>

336
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:56,300
<i>and crawl under the collard fence
