00:28:13,970 --> 00:28:16,730
<i>[ Gasping ]</i>

358
00:28:20,510 --> 00:28:22,740
<i>[ Whimpers ]</i>

359
00:28:43,470 --> 00:28:45,400
<i>Hurry. Hurry.</i>

