387
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:38,470
<i>I'll be back
before you can count to ten.</i>

388
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:42,650
<i>Jem.</i>

389
00:30:48,560 --> 00:30:51,750
<i>One. Two.</i>

390
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:53,990
<i>Three.</i>

391
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:56,120
