392
00:30:57,900 --> 00:30:59,990
<i>Scout?</i>

393
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:02,330
<i>Come on in.</i>

394
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,570
<i>- [ Screen Door Squeaks, Door Closes ]
- Five.</i>

395
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:06,570
<i>Six.</i>

396
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:09,670
<i>Seven.
Eight.</i>

397
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:12,110
<i>Nine.</i>

398
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:14,120
<i>Ten.</i>

399
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:17,440
<i>Eleven.</i>

400
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:19,610
<i>Twelve.</i>

401
00:31:19,690 --> 00:31:21,780
<i>Thirteen.</i>

402
00:31:21,860 --> 00:31:24,330
