403
00:31:24,390 --> 00:31:26,790
<i>[ Dog Barking ]</i>

404
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:30,260
<i>[ Clattering,
Barking Continues ]</i>

405
00:31:30,330 --> 00:31:32,460
<i>Jem!</i>

406
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:37,800
<i>- [ Door Opens, Closes ]
