407
00:31:37,870 --> 00:31:43,640
<i>[ Barking Continues ]</i>

408
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:46,770
<i>[ Aunt Stephanie Yelling ]
What was that? What is it?</i>

409
00:31:46,850 --> 00:31:50,480
<i>What happened?
What happened?</i>

410
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:53,150
<i>What's goin' on?
What is it?</i>

411
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:55,660
<i>Atticus, what is it?</i>

412
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:59,490
<i>Will somebody please tell me
what's goin' on?</i>

413
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:02,160
<i>Uh, Mr. Radley...</i>

414
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:05,260
<i>shot at a prowler out
in his collard patch.</i>

415
00:32:05,330 --> 00:32:07,430
<i>A prowler?
Oh, Maudie!</i>

416
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:10,270
<i>Whoever it was
won't be back anytime soon.</i>

417
00:32:10,340 --> 00:32:12,270
<i>Mr. Radley must have scared them
out of their wits.</i>

418
00:32:12,340 --> 00:32:14,610
<i>- Good night. Good night.
- Good night, Atticus.</i>

419
00:32:14,680 --> 00:32:17,410
<i>Oh, scared the living daylights
out of me.</i>

420
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:20,940
<i>A prowler?
